data.description: This 2022 built home is located on a premium corner homesite and will impress with its open and functional floorplan. This home is complete with 4,367 total square feet including five bedrooms, a large loft, a private study with double french doors, five bathrooms plus a finished basement with rec room. The kitchen boasts upgraded cabinets, quartz countertops, herringbone tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances including a gas range plus large island that opens to the two-story vaulted family room. The spacious primary suite will not disappoint with its large walk-in closet and luxurious bathroom with dual sinks and high-end finishes. This home is better than new with all the finishing touches complete. All appliances and blinds are included. In addition, the property is fully fenced and landscaped. The backyard features and extended patio - perfect for relaxing or entertaining! As if this was not enough, the three car tandem garage offers an additional 688 square feet. Must see!  Attention:  ***This home has a 4.5% assumable interest rate.  Call for details.
